@startuml
title Website Development State Machine Diagram

state StartChoice <<choice>>
state AdminChoice <<choice>>
state EditorChoice <<choice>>
state ReadFeedbackChoice <<choice>>

[*] --> StartChoice

state "Navigate to homepage" as NavigateToHomepage
NavigateToHomepage : entry / User navigates to homepage
NavigateToHomepage : do / Display navigation bar
NavigateToHomepage : exit / Navigation successful

state "Display project information" as DisplayProjectInformation
DisplayProjectInformation : entry / User selects project
DisplayProjectInformation : do / Fetch project details
DisplayProjectInformation : exit / Project information displayed

state "View photos or videos" as ViewPhotosOrVideos
ViewPhotosOrVideos : entry / User chooses to view photos or videos
ViewPhotosOrVideos : do / Display selected content
ViewPhotosOrVideos : exit / Content viewed successfully

state "Display career opportunities" as DisplayCareerOpportunities
DisplayCareerOpportunities : entry / User selects career opportunity
DisplayCareerOpportunities : do / Fetch opportunity details
DisplayCareerOpportunities : exit / Opportunity information displayed

state "Choose to view updates or apply for job/internship" as ChooseToUpdateOrApply
ChooseToUpdateOrApply : entry / User chooses to view updates or apply
ChooseToUpdateOrApply : do / Display selected option
ChooseToUpdateOrApply : exit / Option chosen successfully

state "Check submitted job applications" as CheckSubmittedApplications
CheckSubmittedApplications : entry / System checks for new applications
CheckSubmittedApplications : do / Verify application details
CheckSubmittedApplications : exit / Applications checked successfully

StartChoice --> NavigateToHomepage
NavigateToHomepage --> DisplayProjectInformation
DisplayProjectInformation --> ViewPhotosOrVideos
ViewPhotosOrVideos --> DisplayCareerOpportunities
DisplayCareerOpportunities --> ChooseToUpdateOrApply
ChooseToUpdateOrApply --> CheckSubmittedApplications

CheckSubmittedApplications --> [*]

@enduml
